# Clean-Code-Chapter-2 (naming)


* naming of classes ,variables , function and files


* name is very important for users and programmer


* name of any topic tell the user of program what it used for  


* avoid using number in naming


* use prouncable names  


* dont name variables  as "a"  or "z"   try to put name for it like "Event" 


* dont put data_type in names 


* avoid perfix names
 
 
* class >>>  nouns   function >>> verb 


* Avoid long names 


* first letter  in first word is small and every new word in name is capital 



